title: Ep. #84 | Catching Up: AleXa (알렉사)
description:
Multi-talented solo artist and podcast host AleXa sits down with Eric to discuss her 2nd mini album 'Decoherence'! Find out how AleXa made her way from Tulsa, Oklahoma to Seoul, South Korea and who she stans in the K-pop world.


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
